physical_examinations.relevant_findings: Large head, prominent forehead, beaked nose, craniofacial disproportion, reduced subcutaneous fat, thin skin, rigid joints, right-sided facial palsy, craniosynostosis, scaphocephaly, hazy cornea, inability to close right eye, glaucoma, proptosis, ectopia lentis, talipes calcaneovalgus, bilateral hydronephrosis, ventricular septal defect, long hands and feet, bilateral polydactyly of hands, generalized lipodystrophy, partial syndactyly in the 2nd and 3rd toe, sparse scalp hairs (alopecia), prominent veins.
